name: INSPIRE_Q_Torrington_Linen_Nailhead_Track_Arm_L-Shaped_Configurable_Chaise_Sectional
description:
Update the look of your home with ease with this Torrington collection. Traditional sophistication is lent to the piece, styled with a high back, track arms and nail head detailing. Covered in a white linen, the sectional is the perfect addition to your home.

The dark espresso wood finish gives the piece a classic finishing touch which makes it perfect for your transitional living room or den. Adorn this sectional with several multicolored throw pillows to inject more visual depth and drama to the overall look of the sectional. StyleCasual, Contemporary, ModernMaterialFabric, Linen, MDF, WoodTypeLoveseatAssemblyAssembly RequiredColorWhiteFurniture PatternSolid
